Tower Semiconductor

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Tower Semiconductor Ltd.





TowerJazz headquarters in Migdal Haemek, Israel.




Type

Public


Traded as
TASE: TSEM NASDAQ: TSEM


Industry
Semiconductor


