              TowerJazz offers a broad range of customizable process technologies, including SiGe BiCMOS and RF CMOS for radio frequency and high performance analog (HPA) applications; CMOS image sensor (CIS); power management, including BCD and 700V, and its patented Y-Flash, the leading solution for non-volatile memory (NVM); CMOS; mixed-signal CMOS; and MEMS capabilities.
            
